Package gui

Interface IControl

All Known Implementing Classes:
CEOHomePageController, ConnectToServerController, CreateAccountController, CustomerHomePageController, LoginController, ManagerHomePageController, OrderSummaryController, PickItemsController, PickPickUpTypeController, PickRestuarntController, ReceiveOrderController, SupplierHomePageController, SupplierOrdersPageController, UpdateMenuController, ViewBranchReportsController, ViewCEOQuarterReportsController, ViewCEOReportsController
public interface IControl
Interface for controllers in the application. This interface defines the methods that all controllers should implement, including starting the stage, handling the back button action, and displaying alerts.
Version:
5.0
